### Variables
@baseUrl = https://cactro-15-3-2026.vercel.app/

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/moo

###

### 1. Check current status (Should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me

###

### 2. Login as Manager (Default User - Simple Password)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "organizer@cactro.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

###

### 3. Update Event (As Manager - Triggers Notification Log)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/events/evt-101
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Cactro Tech Summit 2026 (Updated)",
    "description": "An updated description for the demo."
}

###

### 4. Signup a New Customer (Auto-increments ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "newuser3@test.com",
    "password": "securePassword",
    "role": "CUSTOMER"
}

###

### 5. Login as the New Customer (Uses Bcrypt)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "newuser3@test.com",
    "password": "securePassword"
}

###

### 6. Book Event (As Customer - Triggers Email Log)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events/evt-101/book

###

### 7. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout